name: Abandoned
description:
Abandoned

Last piece of my Isometric Series that is all about life contained in a small cube.

"Here is where your soul resides when it needs to rest, to be alone. You just need time to heal... You are not forgotten..."

This piece took a long time to get everything right! It simbolizes mental health and artistic struggles, that sometimes you need time for yourself...

Size of the artwork: 1080 x 1080 px
